data.description: Immerse yourself in this impeccable 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home, nestled in the prestigious Otay Ranch neighborhood. Boasting an open and inviting layout, this residence is a testament to contemporary design and comfort. As you enter, be greeted by fresh, modern paint tones and a newly sealed fence that ensures both privacy and elegance.  The heart of this home is the spacious living area, anchored by a tastefully re-designed fireplace and mantel, creating a perfect backdrop for memorable gatherings. The kitchen, practical yet stylish, comes equipped with a new water heater and microwave, complementing the sleek design and functionality of this culinary space.  The primary bedroom is tranquil, with replaced carpets that add a touch of luxury and comfort. The refined panama shutters not only enhance the aesthetic appeal but also provide serene light control. The guest bath doesn't disappoint either with refreshed cabinets and flooring that resonate with the home's overall charm.  Step outside to find a meticulously maintained yard, laid with crisp turf, inviting you to indulge in the blissful San Diego climate. This home's garage is a standout with epoxy finish that adds durability and style.  Located in a neighborhood celebrated for its verdant surroundings and top-tier schools, this home is not just a residence, but a lifestyle choice for those seeking the perfect balance of luxury and comfort in one of San Diego’s most desirable areas. Your opportunity to own a slice of paradise in Otay Ranch awaits.
